<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            color: #333;
            background: #fff;
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: #e74c3c;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #e74c3c;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .screen-only {
            background: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        
        .print-only {
            display: none;
            background: #2ecc71;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        
        .different-colors {
            background: #f39c12;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        
        .box-shadow-test {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            padding: 1rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: #ecf0f1;
        }
        
        .border-test {
            border: 3px solid #9b59b6;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        
        /* Print-specific styles */
        @media print {
            body {
                margin: 0;
                padding: 1rem;
                background: white;
                color: black;
            }
            
            h1 {
                color: #000;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
            }
            
            .screen-only {
                display: none;
            }
            
            .print-only {
                display: block;
                background: #000;
                color: white;
                -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
                color-adjust: exact;
            }
            
            .different-colors {
                background: #666;
                color: white;
                -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
                color-adjust: exact;
            }
            
            .box-shadow-test {
                box-shadow: none;
                border: 1px solid #000;
                background: #f0f0f0;
            }
            
            .border-test {
                border: 2px solid #000;
            }
        }
        
        @page {
            margin: 1in;
            size: A4;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
        <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Test @media print CSS overrides and print-specific styling</p>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="screen-only">
            <h2>Screen Only Content</h2>
            <p>This section is only visible on screen and will be hidden when printed or converted to PDF.</p>
            <p><strong>CSS:</strong> <code>@media print { .screen-only { display: none; } }</code></p>
        </section>

        <section class="print-only">
            <h2>Print Only Content</h2>
            <p>This section is only visible in print/PDF and hidden on screen.</p>
            <p><strong>CSS:</strong> <code>@media print { .print-only { display: block; } }</code></p>
        </section>

        <section class="different-colors">
            <h2>Different Colors for Print</h2>
            <p>This section has different colors for screen vs print media.</p>
            <p><strong>Screen:</strong> Orange background</p>
            <p><strong>Print:</strong> Gray background (defined in @media print)</p>
        </section>

        <section class="box-shadow-test">
            <h2>Box Shadow Removal</h2>
            <p>This section has a box shadow on screen but uses a border in print for better compatibility.</p>
            <p><strong>Screen:</strong> Drop shadow effect</p>
            <p><strong>Print:</strong> Simple border (shadows removed)</p>
        </section>

        <section class="border-test">
            <h2>Border Adjustments</h2>
            <p>Borders are often adjusted for print to ensure they render clearly.</p>
            <p><strong>Screen:</strong> 3px purple border</p>
            <p><strong>Print:</strong> 2px black border</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Testing Instructions</h2>
            <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0;">
                <thead>
                    <tr style="background: #f8f9fa;">
                        <th style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left;">Test Case</th>
                        <th style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left;">CLI Command</th>
                        <th style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left;">Expected Result</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 0.75rem;">Screen Media</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 0.75rem;"><code>--media-type screen</code></td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 0.75rem;">Blue "Screen Only" section visible</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 0.75rem;">Print Media</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 0.75rem;"><code>--media-type print</code></td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 0.75rem;">Green "Print Only" section visible</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 0.75rem;">Print Backgrounds</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 0.75rem;"><code>--print-background</code></td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 0.75rem;">Background colors preserved</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 0.75rem;">No Backgrounds</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 0.75rem;">Default (no --print-background)</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 0.75rem;">White backgrounds, black text</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer style="margin-top: 3rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem;">
        <p><strong>Print CSS Testing:</strong> Compare screen preview with PDF output to verify @media print styles</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>